terest de manire plus naturelle.</p><p><img src="http://images.2803.fr/uploads/2012/02/pinterest-button-550x524.png" alt="" title="pinterest-button" width="550" height="524" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-14443" /></p><p>Exemple  voir sur le blog deco ou sur design hunting</p><hr\n /><strong>Vous venez de lire la version freemium de l\'article, la version premium (avec les liens) est ici : </strong><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://www.vingthuitzerotrois.fr/wordpress/integrer-bouton-pinterest-sur-son-blog-14442/">Intgrer le bouton Pinterest sur son blog</a><br/>N\'h&eacute;sitez pas &agrave; suivre le compte <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://twitter.com/henrilabarre">Twitter</a> et la page <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://www.facebook.com/vingt.huit.zero.trois">Facebook</a><br/> Copyright &copy; 2005-2010 <strong><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://www.2803media.fr">2803 MEDIA</a></strong><br/><hr\n />";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:12;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:68:"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:60:"ChannelWP : Nouveaux paramtres de confidentialits Google";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:2:"id";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:68:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/HomoSapiensInternetus/~3/IyL66flVQ-4/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:2:{s:3:"rel";s:9:"alternate";s:4:"href";s:68:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/HomoSapiensInternetus/~3/IyL66flVQ-4/";}}s:8:"xml_b